name: load_timestamp
description: The timestamp when the record was loaded.

name: kind
description: Identifies the type of the API resource. For LicenseAssignment resources, the value is admin#licensing#licenseAssignment.

name: userId
description: The unique ID of the user the license is assigned to.

name: productId
description: The product ID of the product the license is for.

name: skuId
description: The SKU ID of the product the license is for.

name: skuName
description: The name of the SKU of the product.
